    public abstract class AbstractPropertyAndPreferencePage
extends org.eclipse.ui.dialogs.PropertyPage
implements org.eclipse.ui.IWorkbenchPropertyPage, org.eclipse.ui.IWorkbenchPreferencePage
    This abstract class permits other properties pages to use some classical method such creating fields openly used.
